data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  Welcome home to this beautifully renovated 3/2 located in the heart of  Marion Oaks. Dawned with an open floor plan you can brag  about, a gorgeously remodeled kitchen with new appliances that will impress all of your guests, and a living room that will  provide plenty of room for all your entertaining needs. NEW roof, NEW AC, New windows that boast natural light throughout the home,  accentuating everything it has to offer. No Carpet! On just over half an acre of land, the backyard has endless potential and is fully  fenced in with a 6-foot privacy fence. This is truly a must-see! More pictures to come.
